summary: A lightweight utility written in C# that let's you manage your ENB installation.
descriptionHtml:
[center][color=#00ffff][font=Comic Sans MS][size=4]ENB Facilitator is a lightweight utility written in C# that lets you manage your ENB installation. It is currently in beta, but I will eventually add the ability to create profiles and much more. Please report any bugs :)
[/size][/font]

[/color][/center][color=#00ffff]
[/color]
author: ThroughDeadlyWaters
